       01  V            PIC 9.
       78  C78          VALUE 'A'.
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
           IF FUNCTION TRIM (' ')
              CONTINUE
              CONTINUE
           END-IF.
           IF CON
              CONTINUE
              CONTINUE
           END-IF.
           IF V
              CONTINUE
              CONTINUE
           END-IF.
